name: In the near Future
description:
Our world is facing several crises that we are commonly surrounded by. Globally it's necessary that we take action through our political regimes.

When collecting this NFT you are lucky to even acquire it in physical format too. The printing of this work of art comes from the latest generation of EPSON printers, with exceptional quality. 12-color Giclée print on 240 gsm fine art pure cotton paper corresponds to museum quality.
